name: Swedish Gymnastics Association 35 Year Plaque
obverse: Bust of a male gymnast facing right inside a circle with a red background. Inscription in 9 lines with engraved name at the bottom.
obverse_inscriptions: SVENSKA GYMNASTIKFÖRBUNDETS PLAKETT FÖR 35-ÅRIGT INTRESSERAT DELTAGANDE I GYNASTIKÖVNINGAR TILL
description: This medal was made by the Swedish Gymnastics Associations to celebrate 35 years of interest in gymnastics.
